---
const tags = ['Social media in progress', 'Visual thinking', 'Canva · CapCut · Photoshop base', 'Modena e dintorni', 'Pronta a imparare'];
---

<section id="top" class="relative overflow-hidden pt-12 sm:pt-16 lg:pt-20">
  <div class="absolute left-6 top-28 h-28 w-28 rounded-full bg-sage/30 blur-3xl dark:bg-sage/20" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="absolute right-0 top-36 h-40 w-40 rounded-full bg-coral/20 blur-3xl dark:bg-coral/20" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <div class="container-page grid items-center gap-12 pb-16 lg:grid-cols-[1.05fr_0.95fr] lg:pb-20">
    <div class="reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow mb-5">Aspirante Social Media Manager · Modena</p>
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold leading-[1.04] sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
        Mente tecnica, spirito creativo. Sto costruendo il mio futuro nei social media.
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-8 text-muted dark:text-nighttext/72">
        Sono Carlotta Della Casa, vivo a Modena e sto trasformando la mia esperienza tra colore, dettagli e ricerca in un nuovo percorso nella comunicazione digitale.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row">
        <a class="button-primary" href="mailto:dellacasacarlotta@gmail.com">Contattami</a>
        <a class="button-secondary" href="/assets/CarlottaDellaCasa_CV.pdf" download>Scarica CV</a>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        {tags.map((tag) => (
          <span class="rounded-full border border-ink/10 bg-white/70 px-3 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-muted dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-white/5 dark:text-nighttext/72">
            {tag}
          </span>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative mx-auto w-full max-w-md reveal [animation-delay:120ms]">
      <div class="absolute -left-5 top-8 h-full w-full rounded-[2rem] bg-apricot dark:bg-coral/70" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="absolute -right-4 -top-4 h-32 w-32 rounded-full bg-lilac/70 blur-sm dark:bg-lilac/40" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <figure class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] border-8 border-white bg-white shadow-soft dark:border-nightcard dark:bg-nightcard">
        <img
          src="/assets/carlotta-profile.jpeg"
          alt="Ritratto di Carlotta Della Casa"
          class="aspect-[4/5] w-full object-cover"
          width="900"
          height="1125"
          loading="eager"
        />
      </figure>
      <div class="absolute -bottom-5 left-6 rounded-lg bg-ink px-4 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-white shadow-glow dark:bg-nighttext dark:text-night">
        Colore, metodo, comunicazione.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
